    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow business entertainment expenses to be offset against corporate tax bills",
        "additional_details": "Currently it is not allowed.\r\n\r\nIf the Government would allow a moratorium on this particular Tax Rule for two years, as of now, it should provide a major boost to the Hospitality Sector and the people employed in that industry.\r\n\r\nIt should also have the effect of money re-circulating as the Hospitality Sector would be earning money and paying tax on the income plus they would be employing people who in turn would be paying tax.",
        "background": "I would like the Government to change Tax Regulations to all, offsetting Business Entertainment Expenses against income.",
